description: Returns all the available versions for the specified Amazon Connect instance and flow identifier.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Connect instance.

nested_items.name: ContactFlowVersionSummaryList
nested_items.description: A list of flow version summaries.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the view version.

nested_items.name: VersionDescription
nested_items.description: The description of the flow version.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: The identifier of the flow version.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, this is the token for the next set of results.
